dct_title_s: Automobile Routes Between Los Angeles and San Diego and connecting roads
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; F.T.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Ooriented with north toward upper right.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways.
Indicates distances from Los Angeles and San Diego.
Los Angeles to San Diego: "Via coast route - 133 miles," "Inland - 174."
Numbered 76 in lower left corner, and 31 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
